\f2\b \cf0 Reasoning:
\f1\b0  Trade counts are not equally informative when outcomes are serially dependent. A calibrated evidence-sufficiency test is more defensible, while visible trade/regime counts keep the limitation understandable.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa200\partightenfactor0

