\f2\b\fs27 \cf0 17.	What must be counted\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa60\partightenfactor0

\fs26 \cf0 Context:
\f1\b0  The system needs honest funnel counts and statistical denominators. A family the agent proposed and rejected is a selection event; a parameter combination that was never evaluated should not be called a tested strategy.\

\f2\b Question:
\f1\b0  Which events must the permanent research ledger distinguish?\

\f2\b Suggested answer:
\f1\b0  Record every proposed family/version, invalid or policy-rejected submission, declared search space, configuration actually cheap-screened, full backtest, validation attempt, feedback-informed batch, and final Gold/rejection. Count only configurations actually evaluated as "tested."\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa80\partightenfactor0

